bio: Fidgephant always feels like his nose is going to leak. He attacks with a water stream when he has to release it all!

soultimate.name: Fidgeting Smack
soultimate.description: Deal massive damage to foes nearby.

skill.effect: When HP falls to 0, will recover once only, at 1 HP.
